00:11:25.476 --> 00:11:28.979
He was scouted even before he graduated.
so he's already living that life.

240
00:11:29.063 --> 00:11:32.108
Look. I'll show you.
Here. take a look at this.

241
00:11:33.109 --> 00:11:36.946
An expensive motorcycle. hard liquor.
designer clothes. tattoos.

242
00:11:37.029 --> 00:11:39.657
And. according to the kids.
there are rumors going around

243
00:11:39.740 --> 00:11:42.493
that he's already earning
tens of millions of won each month.

244
00:11:42.576 --> 00:11:45.162
I get why they're not motivated to study.

245
00:11:45.246 --> 00:11:48.791
They're all killing themselves fighting
so Gwon-hyeok will scout them too.

246
00:11:48.874 --> 00:11:50.084
[jaunty music plays]

247
00:11:50.167 --> 00:11:51.085
[man sighs]

248
00:11:53.045 --> 00:11:54.714
Just fucking die. you bastard!

249
00:11:54.797 --> 00:11:56.132
[groans]

250
00:11:56.966 --> 00:11:58.342
[Seong-hwan groans]

251
00:11:58.926 --> 00:12:02.763
You motherfucker. Your stupid mouth
will always be your weakness.

252
00:12:02.847 --> 00:12:05.433
-Whoa! Hold on. guys! Holy fuck!
-What is it?

253
00:12:05.516 --> 00:12:06.809
-[Jik-sae] Whoa! Fuck!
-What?

254
00:12:06.892 --> 00:12:08.686
Gwon-hyeok sent you a DM! Check it out!

255
00:12:08.769 --> 00:12:10.312
[weapon clatters]

256
00:12:11.063 --> 00:12:12.314
LET'S HAVE AN INTERVIEW

257
00:12:13.441 --> 00:12:15.276
It's Gwon-hyeok! He messaged me!

258
00:12:15.985 --> 00:12:19.363
He wants to have an interview with me.
you fucking asshole. Yes!

259
00:12:19.447 --> 00:12:20.573
[cheering]

260
00:12:20.656 --> 00:12:23.409
-Shit! Fuck! Fuck!
-[In-beom] Whoo!

261
00:12:23.492 --> 00:12:26.287
I'm telling you. our teaching staff
simply can't handle them anymore.

262
00:12:26.370 --> 00:12:29.331
And. um. that's why we contacted the ERPB.

263
00:12:29.415 --> 00:12:30.249
[music stops]

264
00:12:30.875 --> 00:12:33.711
So. when will the other inspectors
from the organization get here?

265
00:12:33.794 --> 00:12:35.838
Should we find a place to set you all up?

266
00:12:35.921 --> 00:12:37.548
Oh. no need. It's just me.

267
00:12:38.048 --> 00:12:39.884
You're gonna handle them
all on your own. then?

268
00:12:40.468 --> 00:12:41.469
I don't want to scare you.

269
00:12:41.552 --> 00:12:44.263
but our last gym teacher
was a former national judo athlete.

270
00:12:44.346 --> 00:12:46.515
He tried to break up a fight
and broke his collarbone.

271
00:12:46.599 --> 00:12:48.100
He hasn't been back to school since.

272
00:12:48.184 --> 00:12:51.812
This is way more than simple discipline.
You need to prepare yourself for war.

273
00:12:51.896 --> 00:12:54.315
Damn! Do you really think
war is necessary?

274
00:12:54.398 --> 00:12:57.651
I'm telling you. with that kind of
laid-back attitude. you're in big trouble.

275
00:12:57.735 --> 00:12:59.904
You should. uh. just look at it
like it's a war. and--

276
00:12:59.987 --> 00:13:02.656
Sir. look. If we go to war…

277
00:13:02.740 --> 00:13:03.699
[inhales]

278
00:13:03.783 --> 00:13:05.034
…then people will die.

279
00:13:10.456 --> 00:13:11.457
[Hwa-jin sighs]

280
00:13:11.540 --> 00:13:13.167
[tense music plays]

281
00:13:15.586 --> 00:13:16.420
[Hwa-jin exhales]

282
00:13:16.504 --> 00:13:17.588
[Hwa-jin sniffs]

283
00:13:17.671 --> 00:13:18.631
[Hwa-jin sighs]

284
00:13:20.257 --> 00:13:21.467
Don't worry about it.

285
00:13:21.967 --> 00:13:25.304
Your students will all get along
and they'll enjoy their classes.

286
00:13:26.639 --> 00:13:29.517
[groaning]

287
00:13:30.142 --> 00:13:31.352
[boy groans]

288
00:13:32.311 --> 00:13:34.021
-[groans]
-[Seong-hwan] Goddamn it.

289
00:13:34.104 --> 00:13:36.357
Blah. blah. blah. blah. blah. blah.

290
00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:38.484
You're a piece of crap. you fucking idiot.

291
00:13:38.567 --> 00:13:42.071
You ran away before. didn't you?
Why'd you come to this school anyway?

292
00:13:44.323 --> 00:13:47.159
I wanted to study cars
and get a job somewhere.

293
00:13:47.243 --> 00:13:49.328
I'm trying to get a job. too. you know.

294
00:13:49.411 --> 00:13:51.580
Gwon-hyeok is his own corporation.

295
00:13:52.164 --> 00:13:54.416
and fist fights are what we get graded on.

296
00:14:05.970 --> 00:14:07.888
AUTOMOTIVE TECHNICIAN
PRACTICAL TEST

297
00:14:10.641 --> 00:14:11.642
Get over here.

298
00:14:11.725 --> 00:14:14.103
Hey! Transfer student. come here.

299
00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:15.437
-[laughter]
-Move your ass!

300
00:14:16.021 --> 00:14:17.064
-Get over there.
-Wait!

301
00:14:17.147 --> 00:14:18.232
What? What did…

302
00:14:18.315 --> 00:14:19.400
You can beat him. right?

303
00:14:20.234 --> 00:14:22.111
-Fight.
-Huh?

304
00:14:22.611 --> 00:14:24.113
The fucker that loses

305
00:14:24.613 --> 00:14:25.698
will become the punch meter.

306
00:14:25.781 --> 00:14:28.659
[laughter]

307
00:14:29.159 --> 00:14:32.079
Uh. do you think I could ask you what…

308
00:14:32.913 --> 00:14:33.873
what is a punch meter?

309
00:14:34.665 --> 00:14:36.333
-You wanna know. hey?
-[laughter]

310
00:14:36.417 --> 00:14:37.293
[Geun-dae] Oh.

311
00:14:37.793 --> 00:14:39.628
-Lose and find out.
-Oh.

312
00:14:40.296 --> 00:14:41.297
Fight.

313
00:14:42.673 --> 00:14:43.674
Oh.

314
00:14:44.633 --> 00:14:46.135
-Want me to kick your ass?
-[whimpers]

315
00:14:46.218 --> 00:14:49.513
What? Wait!
Wh… what are you doing? [pants]

316
00:14:49.597 --> 00:14:51.807
-[indistinct chatter]
-Just hit me.

317
00:14:51.891 --> 00:14:54.310
-Why today? Why are you doing this?
-They always do this.

318
00:14:54.393 --> 00:14:55.769
-Hit me.
-No. I can't!

319
00:14:55.853 --> 00:14:57.730
If you don't.
they'll beat the both of us up.

320
00:14:57.813 --> 00:14:59.356
[grunts]

321
00:14:59.440 --> 00:15:01.108
-[cheering]
-Oh!

322
00:15:01.775 --> 00:15:03.777
-[boy 1] Get him up!
-Are you okay?

323
00:15:03.861 --> 00:15:04.945
-[Seong-hwan grunts]
-Whoa!

324
00:15:05.529 --> 00:15:06.947
-[groans]
-[Seong-hwan] Listen to me.

325
00:15:07.031 --> 00:15:09.783
If Gwon-hyeok doesn't notice us
this time around.

326
00:15:09.867 --> 00:15:11.410
then we're all done for.

327
00:15:11.493 --> 00:15:12.870
-Okay. Got it.
-Punch meter?

328
00:15:13.454 --> 00:15:15.039
[breathes heavily]

329
00:15:16.582 --> 00:15:18.834
[boy 2] Make sure
you measure the distance properly!

330
00:15:18.918 --> 00:15:21.587
-[groans]
-[students] Ooh!

331
00:15:22.588 --> 00:15:24.590
<i>♪ Bada-bada-ba-bam! </i>♪

332
00:15:24.673 --> 00:15:25.883
You scored 92 points.

333
00:15:25.966 --> 00:15:27.718
Congratulations.
You must be an MMA fighter.

334
00:15:27.801 --> 00:15:29.970
[Seong-hwan] You've improved.
You should fight with them.

335
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:31.013
[laughter]

336
00:15:31.096 --> 00:15:33.474
[boy 3] How many points do I get?
Move. move.

337
00:15:33.557 --> 00:15:35.100
-[grunting]
-[cheering]

338
00:15:35.684 --> 00:15:38.687
You scored 95 points!
Congrats. You're currently number one!

339
00:15:38.771 --> 00:15:39.855
-[boy 4] Ha!
-[boy 5] Fuck!

340
00:15:39.939 --> 00:15:40.981
[panting]

341
00:15:41.065 --> 00:15:43.400
[laughter fades]

342
00:15:43.484 --> 00:15:45.569
[breathes heavily]

343
00:15:46.445 --> 00:15:48.405
Oh. whoa. whoa. whoa!
Uh. hey. are you okay?

344
00:15:48.489 --> 00:15:49.448
I'm okay.

345
00:15:49.531 --> 00:15:50.574
-Oh.
-Don't worry about it.

346
00:15:50.658 --> 00:15:52.326
-Oh. well. here. just…
-[groans]

347
00:15:52.409 --> 00:15:56.288
Just hold on to this for a sec.
At least let me hold your bag for you.

348
00:15:56.372 --> 00:15:58.123
-It's really all right.
-I want to help.

349
00:15:58.916 --> 00:15:59.875
You helped me today.

350
00:16:01.710 --> 00:16:06.090
-Well. thank you.
-So. where do you… where do you live?

351
00:16:06.674 --> 00:16:08.676
[gentle music plays]

352
00:16:09.468 --> 00:16:10.886
[Hyeong-ju] This is my place.

353
00:16:11.553 --> 00:16:13.097
Oh. Right. Here.

354
00:16:13.722 --> 00:16:15.599
-Thanks a lot.
-See you tomorrow.

355
00:16:16.100 --> 00:16:18.018
Do you want to come inside?

356
00:16:19.937 --> 00:16:22.815
[laughs] I didn't mean it like that!
I meant do you want some <i>ramyeon</i>?

357
00:16:22.898 --> 00:16:25.192
Uh… [laughs awkwardly]

358
00:16:25.275 --> 00:16:26.777
Well…

359
00:16:27.528 --> 00:16:28.570
Okay. sure.

360
00:16:28.654 --> 00:16:30.030
-[Hyeong-ju] Great. Come in.
-Okay.

361
00:16:31.115 --> 00:16:32.908
-Watch your step.
-[Geun-dae] Thanks.

362
00:16:32.992 --> 00:16:34.159
[keys jangle]

363
00:16:35.911 --> 00:16:37.246
[door opens]

364
00:16:59.935 --> 00:17:01.478
-[Geun-dae] Uh… Oh.
-[exhales]

365
00:17:01.562 --> 00:17:02.563
Thank you.

366
00:17:03.397 --> 00:17:05.190
So. why did you come to our school?

367
00:17:06.275 --> 00:17:08.652
For college. Through that. uh. special.

368
00:17:08.736 --> 00:17:10.696
uh. specialized high school stream.

369
00:17:11.196 --> 00:17:13.282
Might as well go to another school. then.

370
00:17:14.116 --> 00:17:16.994
Since you just transferred over.
you'll still have a chance.

371
00:17:17.745 --> 00:17:21.331
It's not too late to tell your parents
and get them to enroll you somewhere else.

372
00:17:21.832 --> 00:17:23.167
Oh. thank you.

373
00:17:24.626 --> 00:17:26.003
What about you?

374
00:17:26.545 --> 00:17:29.214
I always thought this school
was my only option. but it wasn't.

375
00:17:29.298 --> 00:17:31.759
Except that now.
it's too late for me to change.

376
00:17:31.842 --> 00:17:33.927
Well. you could always
take the GED instead.

377
00:17:34.011 --> 00:17:37.097
Yes. but that would cost too much
with private academies and tutoring.

378
00:17:46.857 --> 00:17:48.358
-Try some of the kimchi.
-[Geun-dae] Hm?

379
00:17:48.442 --> 00:17:51.070
My mom works at a restaurant.
and the kimchi's famous. apparently.

380
00:17:51.153 --> 00:17:52.196
Okay.

381
00:17:54.740 --> 00:17:55.783
[door opens]

382
00:17:56.492 --> 00:17:57.659
That's my mom.

383
00:17:58.619 --> 00:18:00.454
[mom] Hyeong-ju. are you home?

384
00:18:02.372 --> 00:18:03.248
Good afternoon.

385
00:18:03.332 --> 00:18:06.460
Oh my! Hyeong-ju.
you brought a friend home!

386
00:18:07.836 --> 00:18:11.757
Wait. all you're eating is <i>ramyeon?</i>
Hang on. I'll make a proper meal for you.

387
00:18:12.299 --> 00:18:14.510
-Oh. I'm okay.
-Mom. we'll eat this. it's okay.

388
00:18:15.010 --> 00:18:17.346
-I must smell pretty bad. don't I?
-No.

389
00:18:17.429 --> 00:18:21.183
I'll… I'll go wash up quickly.
Just give me a minute. [chuckles]

390
00:18:21.266 --> 00:18:22.309
[Hyeong-ju chuckles]

391
00:18:23.143 --> 00:18:24.520
-[door closes]
-[chuckles]

392
00:18:27.106 --> 00:18:29.024
[paper rustles]

393
00:18:41.078 --> 00:18:43.080
[chuckles] If you stuff them like this.

394
00:18:43.163 --> 00:18:45.791
the newspaper picks up all the moisture.
so it dries well.

395
00:18:45.874 --> 00:18:49.711
My mom's shoes stay wet all day long
so it gets uncomfortable. [chuckles]

396
00:18:56.593 --> 00:18:57.594
[music fades]

397
00:19:00.848 --> 00:19:02.015
[indistinct chatter]

398
00:19:02.099 --> 00:19:03.725
[boy 1] Were you sitting
over there before?

399
00:19:04.518 --> 00:19:05.519
[boy 2] Fuck off.

400
00:19:08.647 --> 00:19:12.109
[students] Three. four. five.

401
00:19:13.402 --> 00:19:15.529
-[sighs]
-[Seong-hwan] Everyone. give it a try.

402
00:19:15.612 --> 00:19:16.613
Try it out!

403
00:19:17.406 --> 00:19:21.410
Those thugs beat you up every single day.
so why do you bother to keep showing up?

404
00:19:21.910 --> 00:19:23.579
'Cause it's still school.

405
00:19:23.662 --> 00:19:25.038
[growls softly]

406
00:19:25.122 --> 00:19:26.290
You're a good kid.

407
00:19:26.790 --> 00:19:28.292
-[students] One. two.
-Who are you?

408
00:19:29.251 --> 00:19:30.210
[students] Three.

409
00:19:30.294 --> 00:19:34.131
I'm an ERPB inspector.
And I did a little bit of research on you.

410
00:19:34.214 --> 00:19:37.509
So. want to hear some facts
about Kim Hyeong-ju?

411
00:19:37.593 --> 00:19:38.886
How do you know who I am?

412
00:19:39.386 --> 00:19:42.014
Kid. I just told you. I did some research.

413
00:19:42.097 --> 00:19:43.807
[students laugh]

414
00:19:43.891 --> 00:19:46.602
You should get in there.
Class is starting. [sighs]

415
00:19:47.686 --> 00:19:49.980
Don't worry about a thing.
I'm gonna make sure

416
00:19:50.063 --> 00:19:52.649
that you start learning
despite those guys. All right?

417
00:19:52.733 --> 00:19:54.860
-[boy 3 laughs]
-You can do it. Kim Hyeong-ju.

418
00:19:55.861 --> 00:19:57.738
[students] One. two…

419
00:19:58.739 --> 00:20:01.158
[boy 4] You seriously expected
a receipt for getting mugged?

420
00:20:01.241 --> 00:20:03.035
We have a fucking dumbass here. guys.

421
00:20:03.118 --> 00:20:04.161
[Geun-dae groans]

422
00:20:04.244 --> 00:20:06.330
[boy 4] Comfy? Just stay down there.

423
00:20:07.122 --> 00:20:07.956
Huh?

424
00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:10.042
[boy 5] I saw it. but I just thought…

425
00:20:10.125 --> 00:20:13.128
<i>-One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest.</i>
-Hm?

426
00:20:13.212 --> 00:20:15.672
<i>One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest.</i>

427
00:20:15.756 --> 00:20:16.840
What is that?

428
00:20:16.924 --> 00:20:18.592
You said you would. um… Remember?

429
00:20:18.675 --> 00:20:21.345
You said you'd go "flutter. flutter."
when I said. "Cuckoo's Nest!"

430
00:20:21.428 --> 00:20:22.512
It was our code.

431
00:20:22.596 --> 00:20:23.513
Code?

432
00:20:26.642 --> 00:20:29.353
-[Seong-hwan] Hey!
-[students] Oh!

433
00:20:29.895 --> 00:20:32.272
[Geun-dae] <i>I sent you a video</i>
<i>and messaged you the code.</i>

434
00:20:32.356 --> 00:20:33.941
[Hyeong-ju] <i>♪ Ba-da-ba-ba-ba-bam! ♪</i>

435
00:20:34.024 --> 00:20:35.651
[jaunty music plays]

436
00:20:35.734 --> 00:20:38.528
Oh. Are you Bong Geun-dae.
the deputy director?

437
00:20:38.612 --> 00:20:39.738
Yes. sir.

438
00:20:40.322 --> 00:20:42.908
[Hwa-jin] Okay. I knew I chose
the right person for this job. Wow.

439
00:20:42.991 --> 00:20:44.910
[laughs]

440
00:20:47.454 --> 00:20:48.372
RÉSUMÉ
BONG GEUN-DAE

441
00:20:51.708 --> 00:20:52.709
Hm.

442
00:21:00.592 --> 00:21:01.510
[Hwa-jin] Right.

443
00:21:02.010 --> 00:21:03.971
Look at me. There.

444
00:21:04.763 --> 00:21:07.015
Deputy Director Bong Geun-dae.
can you run?

445
00:21:07.099 --> 00:21:08.934
Uh. why are you taking a…

446
00:21:11.603 --> 00:21:13.689
[indistinct chatter]

447
00:21:13.772 --> 00:21:15.691
Hey! Hey. you shitheads!

448
00:21:17.693 --> 00:21:19.194
[In-beom laughs]

449
00:21:20.737 --> 00:21:21.780
[boy 1] Four Eyes.

450
00:21:25.534 --> 00:21:30.664
Hey. you gangster. punk-ass.
hooligan. idiotic. numbskull shitheads!

451
00:21:30.747 --> 00:21:32.833
[laughs] Yeah. this is for you!

452
00:21:32.916 --> 00:21:36.920
[laughs] You dumb little punks.
Look at what losers you are!

453
00:21:37.004 --> 00:21:39.423
How can you stand living with yourselves?

454
00:21:39.506 --> 00:21:40.382
[laughs]

455
00:21:40.465 --> 00:21:44.094
Whoever catches that fucker
gets 100.000 won. I'm serious. Get him!

456
00:21:44.177 --> 00:21:45.721
Huh? Uh. oh! Oh. no!

457
00:21:45.804 --> 00:21:48.056
[students clamor]

458
00:21:48.140 --> 00:21:49.433
Uh. uh. I'm sorry!

459
00:21:49.516 --> 00:21:50.600
No! No. don't!

460
00:21:50.684 --> 00:21:52.102
All right! I'm not sorry!

461
00:21:52.185 --> 00:21:53.312
[rock music plays]

462
00:21:53.395 --> 00:21:55.772
[yelps] Whoa! Oh!

463
00:22:01.320 --> 00:22:03.322
-[boy 1] Where is he?
-[boy 2] Where'd he go?

464
00:22:03.822 --> 00:22:06.450
[boy 3] Hey! Get the fuck out here.
you stupid fucking coward!

465
00:22:06.992 --> 00:22:09.161
-[boy 4] You scared. fucker?
-[Seong-hwan] Where is he?

466
00:22:09.244 --> 00:22:10.495
[boy 5] You fucking scared?

467
00:22:10.579 --> 00:22:13.415
Hey! I asked you if you were scared.
you chickenshit!

468
00:22:13.915 --> 00:22:16.168
-[boy 6] What the…
-[boy 7] Hey. what the fuck?

469
00:22:17.461 --> 00:22:18.337
Who is that?

470
00:22:20.297 --> 00:22:21.214
[Hwa-jin] Me?

471
00:22:22.007 --> 00:22:24.634
I'm an inspector with
the Educational Rights Protection Bureau.

472
00:22:24.718 --> 00:22:25.844
Educational what? Wh… what…

473
00:22:25.927 --> 00:22:27.929
It's okay. Don't hurt yourself.

474
00:22:28.013 --> 00:22:30.515
He's from that place that
beat up some nerds at Daehan High.

475
00:22:30.599 --> 00:22:33.643
Oh. wow. So Guun High's
not as stupid as it looks.

476
00:22:33.727 --> 00:22:36.104
Someone's paying attention. I approve!

477
00:22:36.188 --> 00:22:39.900
Mister. this isn't the kind of high school
where we care about that shit.

478
00:22:39.983 --> 00:22:41.485
We don't hold back here.

479
00:22:41.568 --> 00:22:44.071
And we don't give a single fuck
