-[bones crack]
-[thug 4 groans]

961
00:45:30.978 --> 00:45:32.312
-[knife slices]
-[thug 5 groans]

962
00:45:36.859 --> 00:45:39.403
<i>-♪ Yeah. I ain't playing around ♪</i>
<i>-♪ I ain't playing around ♪</i>

963
00:45:39.486 --> 00:45:41.238
<i>♪ I'mma take your crown ♪</i>

964
00:45:41.321 --> 00:45:43.532
<i>♪ Man. better run. gonna hunt you down… ♪</i>

965
00:45:43.615 --> 00:45:45.951
[groans]

966
00:45:47.453 --> 00:45:49.747
<i>-♪ I'm gonna hunt you down ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Gonna hunt you ♪</i>

967
00:45:49.830 --> 00:45:52.708
<i>-♪ Yeah. I ain't playing around ♪</i>
<i>-♪ I ain't playing around ♪</i>

968
00:45:52.791 --> 00:45:54.334
<i>♪ I'mma take your crown ♪</i>

969
00:45:54.418 --> 00:45:57.045
<i>♪ Man. better run. gonna hunt you down ♪</i>

970
00:45:57.546 --> 00:45:59.882
<i>♪ Yeah. I be coming for you</i>
<i>Like Hannibal ♪</i>

971
00:45:59.965 --> 00:46:02.634
<i>♪ Uh. I'm a killer. call me a cannibal ♪</i>

972
00:46:02.718 --> 00:46:05.053
<i>♪ Uh. I'mma take your crown ♪</i>

973
00:46:05.137 --> 00:46:07.806
<i>♪ Man better run. gonna hunt you down ♪</i>

974
00:46:16.565 --> 00:46:17.524
[music stops]

975
00:46:19.651 --> 00:46:20.819
[thugs groan]

976
00:46:20.903 --> 00:46:22.488
[Seong-hwan] Wh… what the hell?

977
00:46:23.781 --> 00:46:25.657
Oh! [whimpers]

978
00:46:25.741 --> 00:46:29.244
Sir. I was wrong. okay?
Please spare me. sir!

979
00:46:29.328 --> 00:46:31.246
Sir. I was also wrong! [whimpers]

980
00:46:31.330 --> 00:46:32.372
That isn't it.

981
00:46:33.957 --> 00:46:36.043
[whimpers] Oh. uh…

982
00:46:36.543 --> 00:46:39.213
Then I'll… I'll stop coming to school!

983
00:46:39.296 --> 00:46:40.798
-[whimpers]
-I'll drop out!

984
00:46:40.881 --> 00:46:42.466
That's not it either.

985
00:46:43.342 --> 00:46:46.053
[whimpers]

986
00:46:47.763 --> 00:46:48.806
Think about it.

987
00:46:49.723 --> 00:46:51.892
Who is it
that you should be apologizing to?

988
00:46:52.392 --> 00:46:55.771
[both whimper]

989
00:46:57.147 --> 00:46:58.190
Oh!

990
00:46:59.358 --> 00:47:01.777
-Oh!
-[Seong-hwan] Oh. right! Hey. hey!

991
00:47:01.860 --> 00:47:03.779
Hyeong-ju! Hey. Hyeong-ju!

992
00:47:03.862 --> 00:47:06.949
I'm sorry! Oh. please. Forgive me. please!

993
00:47:07.032 --> 00:47:09.326
-I'm so sorry!
-I'm so sorry!

994
00:47:09.409 --> 00:47:12.371
Hey. please forgive me!
Please spare me. man. Please!

995
00:47:12.454 --> 00:47:15.123
Uh. it's… it's… it's okay. guys.
It's okay. really.

996
00:47:15.207 --> 00:47:16.542
[In-beom] Oh please! [cries]

997
00:47:16.625 --> 00:47:17.751
You don't have to do that.

998
00:47:17.835 --> 00:47:20.337
[Seong-hwan] No. really.
please forgive me. I'm really sorry.

999
00:47:20.420 --> 00:47:22.506
[Seong-hwan sobs]

1000
00:47:27.469 --> 00:47:28.428
Hyeong-ju.

1001
00:47:28.512 --> 00:47:29.346
[Seong-hwan] Please!

1002
00:47:29.429 --> 00:47:30.848
[sobbing continues]

1003
00:47:32.432 --> 00:47:33.725
You sure you're okay?

1004
00:47:43.944 --> 00:47:45.863
[cries]

1005
00:47:50.284 --> 00:47:52.286
[poignant music plays]

1006
00:47:57.749 --> 00:48:00.210
[Seong-hwan] I'm sorry. [cries]

1007
00:48:05.215 --> 00:48:07.968
[cries]

1008
00:48:10.470 --> 00:48:14.099
[sobs]

1009
00:48:18.896 --> 00:48:21.440
[both cry]

1010
00:48:26.820 --> 00:48:28.488
-[Seong-hwan whimpers]
-[In-beom sniffles]

1011
00:48:33.201 --> 00:48:35.162
[Hwa-jin] If you don't want
to take classes. don't.

1012
00:48:35.245 --> 00:48:37.581
If you don't want to study. don't.
It's your life.

1013
00:48:38.290 --> 00:48:39.207
However…

1014
00:48:41.877 --> 00:48:44.463
don't get in the way
of anyone else's life.

1015
00:48:46.048 --> 00:48:49.927
Don't assume that a minute of your life
is the same as anyone else's.

1016
00:48:50.928 --> 00:48:52.512
Even if it may seem like it.

1017
00:48:58.560 --> 00:49:01.480
That knowledge will make
a world of difference in your life.

1018
00:49:12.199 --> 00:49:15.619
-Understand. you brats?
-Yes! [whimpers]

1019
00:49:15.702 --> 00:49:17.371
Speak up. Do you understand or not?

1020
00:49:17.454 --> 00:49:18.580
[students] Yes. sir!

1021
00:49:23.543 --> 00:49:24.586
[clicks tongue]

1022
00:49:25.587 --> 00:49:26.922
[sirens wail]

1023
00:49:27.547 --> 00:49:28.548
[chuckles]

1024
00:49:33.136 --> 00:49:37.224
[Gang-seok] I will now give a report
on the recent endeavors of the ERPB.

1025
00:49:37.307 --> 00:49:40.477
Through the diligent work
of Inspector Na Hwa-jin.

1026
00:49:40.560 --> 00:49:43.897
the Bureau has resolved the issues
around the right to learn at Guun Tech.

1027
00:49:43.981 --> 00:49:46.900
In order to prevent those issues
from recurring anywhere else.

1028
00:49:46.984 --> 00:49:49.861
we will be contacting departments
to implement the following.

1029
00:49:49.945 --> 00:49:50.821
TATTOO REMOVAL CLINIC

1030
00:49:50.904 --> 00:49:54.241
<i>Starting now. all tattoos will be banned</i>
<i>at all schools.</i>

1031
00:49:54.324 --> 00:49:55.200
[student groans]

1032
00:49:55.283 --> 00:49:57.369
[man] You're gonna do more damage
if you keep moving.

1033
00:49:57.995 --> 00:50:01.123
[Gang-seok] <i>Motorcycles will no longer</i>
<i>be permitted on school grounds.</i>

1034
00:50:01.206 --> 00:50:02.374
NO SMOKING ON CAMPUS

1035
00:50:02.457 --> 00:50:05.544
YOU'LL BE A GREAT MECHANIC
YOUR FRIEND. GEUN-DAE

1036
00:50:05.627 --> 00:50:08.130
[uplifting music plays]

1037
00:50:11.299 --> 00:50:14.803
[Gang-seok] <i>If any student attempts</i>
<i>to start or join an organized crime group.</i>

1038
00:50:14.886 --> 00:50:17.514
<i>like a gang of school bullies</i>
<i>or a gang of violent criminals.</i>

1039
00:50:17.597 --> 00:50:21.935
<i>they will be charged and tried as adults</i>
<i>under the laws against organized crime.</i>

1040
00:50:22.602 --> 00:50:24.813
Finally. in cooperation
with the Ministry of Justice

1041
00:50:24.896 --> 00:50:27.441
and the Ministry
of Sciences and Technology.

1042
00:50:27.524 --> 00:50:31.820
we plan on monitoring and deterring
any Millennial and Gen Z gangsters.

1043
00:50:31.903 --> 00:50:33.447
who recruit through social media.

1044
00:50:33.530 --> 00:50:35.407
<i>We at the ERPB</i>

1045
00:50:35.991 --> 00:50:39.828
<i>will continue to do our utmost to protect</i>
<i>our students' educational rights.</i>

1046
00:50:39.911 --> 00:50:41.705
-TV off!
-[Geun-dae] Oh. yes. sir!

1047
00:50:41.788 --> 00:50:42.956
[Hwa-jin] Whoa!

1048
00:50:43.040 --> 00:50:47.294
You were just in there. and now
you've appeared in here. [laughs]

1049
00:50:47.377 --> 00:50:50.714
I don't mean to overstep. but are you
trying to become a television personality?

1050
00:50:50.797 --> 00:50:52.841
What? You do it. then.

1051
00:50:52.924 --> 00:50:55.469
I didn't mean it like that.
You seem to be enjoying it. that's all.

1052
00:50:55.552 --> 00:50:56.803
Am I not allowed to enjoy it?

1053
00:50:56.887 --> 00:50:59.097
Of course you are! Did you watch him?

1054
00:50:59.181 --> 00:51:02.225
"The Educational Rights Protection Bureau
will do the utmost to protect--"

1055
00:51:02.309 --> 00:51:04.895
-Come on.
-[Hwa-jin] That was the best! [laughs]

1056
00:51:04.978 --> 00:51:08.899
Uh. may I interrupt your conversation
for a moment. please?

1057
00:51:08.982 --> 00:51:09.858
[Gang-seok] Of course.

1058
00:51:09.941 --> 00:51:13.945
Well. I had a few incidental expenses
on this project that were out of pocket.

1059
00:51:14.029 --> 00:51:17.532
Oh. well. of course you should claim
those expenses. What are they?

1060
00:51:17.616 --> 00:51:22.329
Well. uh. on three separate occasions.
I was shaken down.

1061
00:51:22.412 --> 00:51:23.955
Oh. you were? Right.

1062
00:51:24.623 --> 00:51:26.458
Uh. it was 40.000 won in cash

1063
00:51:26.541 --> 00:51:29.294
and 500 from a vending machine
that sold fancy coffees.

1064
00:51:29.377 --> 00:51:31.088
and then. in front
of the labs at the school.

1065
00:51:31.171 --> 00:51:35.884
they took my Nike Air Force shoes.
worth. uh. 125.000 won.

1066
00:51:35.967 --> 00:51:38.595
-They were nice and white and new.
-Mm.

1067
00:51:38.678 --> 00:51:41.973
I had also been microwaving
an Uiseong Garlic Sausage sandwich.

1068
00:51:42.057 --> 00:51:44.935
which was 2.200 won
at the concession stand.

1069
00:51:45.018 --> 00:51:46.103
[jaunty music plays]

1070
00:51:46.186 --> 00:51:48.188
They even took that away from me.

1071
00:51:48.814 --> 00:51:50.148
After calculating everything.

1072
00:51:50.232 --> 00:51:53.944
the total was about 167.000 won
out of pocket.

1073
00:51:54.027 --> 00:51:57.197
So. would I be able to claim that?

1074
00:51:57.864 --> 00:51:58.824
Oh. sure.

1075
00:51:59.574 --> 00:52:01.451
But did they steal anything else?

1076
00:52:01.535 --> 00:52:03.662
Oh. uh…

1077
00:52:03.745 --> 00:52:05.247
MEDICAL BILLS…

1078
00:52:05.330 --> 00:52:06.832
No. that was all of it.

1079
00:52:08.083 --> 00:52:10.210
All right. Claim the expenses.

1080
00:52:10.794 --> 00:52:11.920
[Geun-dae] Thank you. sir.

1081
00:52:15.799 --> 00:52:17.300
Want me to buy you a sausage?

1082
00:52:18.176 --> 00:52:20.929
Huh? Oh. no. no. No. I'm fine. sir.

1083
00:52:21.012 --> 00:52:23.056
That Uiseong Garlic thing
sounds really good.

1084
00:52:23.807 --> 00:52:26.351
-You should have one.
-Hey. lay off.

1085
00:52:26.434 --> 00:52:29.354
-I thought… You just said he was robbed.
-[Gang-seok] Enough.

1086
00:52:30.689 --> 00:52:31.773
[music stops]

1087
00:52:39.447 --> 00:52:40.448
[inhales]

1088
00:52:44.452 --> 00:52:45.287
[sighs]

1089
00:53:12.355 --> 00:53:13.773
[exhales]

1090
00:53:34.211 --> 00:53:35.962
[poignant music plays]

1091
00:54:05.867 --> 00:54:08.286
[haunting ballad plays]

1092
00:55:18.356 --> 00:55:19.441
[music fades]

1093
